		<title>“Nature-first” mining could create $3.5 trillion market by 2030 — report</title>
		<link>https://www.mining.com/nature-first-mining-could-create-3-5-trillion-market-by-2030-report/</link>
					<comments>https://www.mining.com/nature-first-mining-could-create-3-5-trillion-market-by-2030-report/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Cecilia Jamasmie]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2020 22:01:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Careers]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[News]]></category>
